# Build stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jdk-alpine AS builder
WORKDIR /build
COPY pom.xml .
COPY src ./src

# Runtime stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine
RUN apk add --no-cache fontconfig ttf-dejavu curl && \
    curl -sS https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/global/global-bundle.pem -o /tmp/aws-rds-ca.pem && \
    curl -sS https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt.pem -o /tmp/azure-digicert-ca.crt && \
    keytool -importcert -trustcacerts -file /tmp/aws-rds-ca.pem -alias aws-rds-root -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    keytool -importcert -trustcacerts -file /tmp/azure-digicert-ca.crt -alias azure-digicert-root -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm -f /tmp/aws-rds-ca.pem /tmp/azure-digicert-ca.crt && \
    addgroup -g 1001 app && \
    adduser -D -u 1001 -G app app

COPY --from=builder /build/app.jar /app/app.jar
RUN chown -R app:app /app

USER app
WORKDIR /app

EXPOSE 3000

LABEL maintainer="devops@example.com" version="1.0.0" description="Java analytics dashboard"

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD ["curl", "-f", "http://localhost:3000/api/health"]

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
